    // About page hero
    about_pg_title: "About Us",
    about_pg_sub: "Journey with no distance",
    about_hero_eyebrow: "Journey with no distance",
    about_hero_h1: "Northeast Vietnam<br /><span class='text-primary'>Where Stones Bloom</span>",
    about_hero_sapo: "My name is An, and I was born and raised in Ha Giang, the northernmost province of Vietnam. Growing up here, I have witnessed my hometown transform year after year—from one of Vietnam’s poorest and most remote provinces into a destination admired by travelers from all over the world.<br><br>Ha Giang has never been a place of luxury, but it has always been rich in culture, breathtaking landscapes, and resilient people. For generations, life here was challenging, with most families relying on farming to make a living. Everything began to change thanks to the pioneers who introduced and developed the Ha Giang Loop—a journey that has become one of Southeast Asia’s most iconic motorcycle adventures.<br><br>The winding mountain passes, dramatic hairpin bends, towering limestone peaks, and untouched natural beauty have inspired countless travelers to visit Ha Giang. More importantly, tourism has created opportunities for local people, providing jobs, improving livelihoods, and giving many families—including my own—a brighter future.<br><br>That is why I decided to create Horse Loop.<br><br>Horse Loop is more than just a tour company. It is my dream of sharing the beauty of my hometown with travelers from around the world while creating authentic, safe, and unforgettable experiences. At the same time, I hope our work can support local communities, preserve traditional culture, and protect the natural beauty that makes Ha Giang so special.<br><br>When you travel with Horse Loop, you’re not simply visiting famous landmarks.<br><br>You’ll ride through spectacular mountain roads, pass peaceful ethnic villages, and witness the incredible Tu Sản Canyon, one of the deepest canyons in Southeast Asia. You’ll meet local ethnic minority communities, taste traditional cuisine, discover unique customs and traditions, and experience the genuine hospitality that the people of Ha Giang are known for.<br><br>I believe the most memorable journeys are not only about beautiful scenery—they are about the people you meet, the stories you hear, and the moments that stay with you long after you’ve returned home.<br><br>While motorcycle tours remain our specialty, Horse Loop is also developing car tours for families, older travelers, and anyone who prefers a more comfortable way to experience Ha Giang without missing its incredible beauty. I believe everyone should have the opportunity to explore this remarkable region in the way that suits them best.<br><br>As someone born and raised in Ha Giang, I feel incredibly proud of my hometown. Every tour we organize is more than just a trip—it is our way of promoting sustainable tourism, supporting local families, and helping preserve the culture and traditions that define this extraordinary place.<br><br>Thank you for taking the time to read my story.<br><br>I sincerely hope to welcome you to Ha Giang someday. Together with Horse Loop, let’s create memories that will last a lifetime and continue protecting the beauty and spirit of this incredible land for future generations.<br><br>Welcome to Ha Giang. Welcome to Horse Loop.",
    about_pg_desc: "Coming to Ha Giang and Cao Bang, you are not just taking a trip, but embarking on an adventure through the most rugged and majestic mountain passes in Vietnam. In the <strong>Northeast</strong>, we believe that every curve of Ma Pi Leng, every splash of white water at Ban Gioc Waterfall carries a story within.",

    // Tour detail page
